cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CC 

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on the syntactic structure of sentences. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the performance of recurrent neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of neural networks also suggests the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with error rates and patterns, which could fall under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) or computational complexity (cs.CC).
